<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Spark N Snack — curated boxes to spark joy and faith, created by Gracie & Sabreana. Inspiring creative growth and fun connections.">
    <title>Spark N Snack | Inspire. Create. Connect.</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://via.placeholder.com/64" type="image/jpeg">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff7f50;
            --secondary-color: #fff3e6;
            --text-color: #333;
            --bg-color: #f9f9f9;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        header img {
            max-width: 160px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: white;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
        }

        .description {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .description h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .product-showcase {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .product {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .product:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
        }

        .product img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: #eee;
        }

        .product h3 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .value-proposition {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .value-proposition h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .value-proposition ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 2rem auto 0;
        }

        .value-proposition li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .value-proposition li::before {
            content: "★";
            color: var(--primary-color);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        .subscription-form {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .subscription-form h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        label {
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #eee;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #eee;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/180" alt="Spark N Snack Logo">
    <h1>Spark N Snack</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <section class="description">
        <h2>About Spark N Snack</h2>
        <p>
            Spark N Snack is a faith-centered, creativity-fueled subscription brand
            created by Gracie and Sabreana. Each box is designed to spark joy,
            encourage growth, and remind you that you’re not alone on your journey.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="product-showcase">

        <div class="product">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Spark Box">
            <h3>The Spark Box</h3>
            <p>Creative DIY projects, journaling prompts, and inspiration.</p>
            <div class="price">$35</div>
        </div>

        <div class="product">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Spirit Box">
            <h3>The Spirit Box</h3>
            <p>Devotionals, prayer tools, and encouragement for spiritual growth.</p>
            <div class="price">$45</div>
        </div>

        <div class="product">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Combo Delight">
            <h3>The Combo Delight</h3>
            <p>Both boxes combined, plus exclusive behind-the-scenes content.</p>
            <div class="price">$60</div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="value-proposition">
        <h2>Why Spark N Snack?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Faith and creativity blended intentionally</li>
            <li>Curated personally by Gracie & Sabreana</li>
            <li>Encouragement that meets you where you are</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="subscription-form">
        <h2>Join the Community</h2>
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Name</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your name">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Email</label>
                <input type="email" placeholder="you@email.com">
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Subscribe (Coming Soon)</button>
        </form>
    </section>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Spark N Snack — Created by Gracie & Sabreana</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
